</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="111.[188,524,506,558]" box="[229,483,536,558]" pageId="111" pageNumber="112">
<heading box="[229,483,536,558]" centered="true" fontSize="10" level="2" pageId="111" pageNumber="112" reason="4">(figs. 54D, 55D, 56C)</heading>
</paragraph>
